aiImpact.summary: AI tools are increasingly used in web development for tasks like code generation, automated testing, and UI design.  While not immediately threatening, Varun should familiarize himself with these tools to enhance efficiency and remain competitive.  The impact on his role will be gradual, with increased automation of certain tasks but also the creation of new opportunities related to AI integration in web applications.

recommendations: Focus on improving JavaScript proficiency to a more advanced level.
Build a more extensive portfolio showcasing a wider range of projects and technologies.
Actively participate in open-source projects to gain experience and network with other developers.
Explore frameworks like React, Angular, or Vue.js to enhance job prospects.
Seek out mentorship opportunities from experienced web developers.
